      "type": "text",
      "headline": "IP Camera NVR for MSX",
      "text": "Version: 1.0.0\n\nA lightweight IP camera viewer for Media Station X.\n\nFeatures:\n• View up to 8 IP cameras simultaneously\n• Support for RTSP/RTMP camera streams\n• Manual camera addition with credentials\n• Network camera discovery\n• Auto-reconnect on stream failure\n\nBackend powered by RTSPtoWeb.\n\nRequirements:\n• RTSPtoWeb server running on port 8083\n• IP cameras with RTSP/RTMP support\n\nFor support and updates, visit:\nhttps://github.com/benzac-de/msx"
